    </p></td>
    <td colspan=3D"1" rowspan=3D"1" valign=3D"TOP">=20
      <p align=3D"CENTER"><b>in millimhos/cm</b>
    </p></td>
  </tr>
  <tr valign=3D"TOP">=20
